data.title: QWERTY
data.meta_description: "QWERTY" is a song by American band Linkin Park. Recorded during Minutes to Midnight sessions in 2006, it was featured on the sixth exclusive album for the band's fanclub, Linkin Park Underground v6.0. After eighteen years of its first appearance, "QWERTY" was officially released through digital...
